title: Cardano DEX Minswap Sees Volume Jump Driven by SNEK, BANK Meme Coins
description: Volumes surged from just over $1 million at the start of May to $18 million on Tuesday, data from Minswap shows.

title: TrigonX plans to relaunch after overcoming $50 Million debts
description: TrigonX, an Australian crypto exchange that collapsed in December 2022 with significant debts exceeding $50 million, is poised for a revival after creditors approved a deed of company arrangement.
